  29,38,"wahlkna eadana wthmwd, waqad tabayan lakum min masakinihim kharabuha wkhlawha mnhm, whlwl nqmtna bihim jmyeana, whssan lahum alshaytan 'aemalahum alqbyht, fsddahm ean sabil allah waean tariq al'iiman bih wbrslh, wakanuu mustabsirin fi kufruhum wdlalhm, mejbyn bh, yahsabun 'anahum ealaa hudana wswab, baynama hum fi aldalal gharqwn"
